---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
---
<Layout title="Privacy Policy">
    <Header />
    <main class="main-content">
        <section class="content-section safe-zone">
            <div class="container">
                <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
                <p>Last Updated: February 26, 2026</p>
                <p>Welcome to my personal website. Your privacy is important to me. This policy explains how I handle data when you visit this site.</p>
                <h2>1. Information I Collect</h2>
                <p>To provide a better browsing experience, I may collect the following:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Information You Provide:</strong> When you fill out a contact form, subscribe to a newsletter, or leave a comment, you may provide your name, email address, and any other details you enter.</li>
                    <li><strong>Information Collected Automatically:</strong> When you visit this site, server logs or third-party services may record your IP address, browser type, operating system, referring pages, and access times.</li>
                </ul>
                <h2>2. Use of Third-Party Services</h2>
                <p>This site uses the following third-party services, which may collect information via cookies or other technologies (governed by their respective privacy policies):</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Analytics Tools: (e.g., Google Analytics or Cloudflare) to monitor traffic and optimize performance.</li>
                    <li>External Resources: (e.g., Google Fonts, CDN resources) which may log connection data when loading assets.</li>
                    <li>Social/Payment Plugins: Any interaction with social sharing buttons or donation links may be tracked by those respective platforms.</li>
                </ul>
                <h2>3. Handling of Form Data</h2>
                <p>If you submit a form on this website:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Purpose:</strong> The data is used solely to respond to your inquiries, provide requested services, or send subscribed content.</li>
                    <li><strong>Storage:</strong> Data is stored securely and will not be kept longer than necessary, unless required by law.</li>
                    <li><strong>Sharing:</strong> I will never sell, rent, or abuse your personal contact information.</li>
                </ul>
                <h2>4. Your Rights (GDPR & PIPL)</h2>
                <p>Depending on your location, you have certain rights regarding your data:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Right to Access & Rectify:</strong> You can ask what data I hold about you or request corrections.</li>
                    <li><strong>Right to Erasure:</strong> You may request that I delete your form submission records.</li>
                    <li><strong>Withdraw Consent:</strong> You can withdraw consent at any time by clearing cookies or ceasing use of the site.</li>
                </ul>
                <h2>5. Data Security</h2>
                <p>As a personal site, I use standard encryption (such as HTTPS/SSL) to protect data in transit. However, please note that no method of transmission over the internet is 100% secure.</p>
                <h2>6. Contact Me</h2>
                <p>If you have questions or wish to exercise your data rights, please contact me at:</p>
                <p>Email: E-Crepuscular@outlook.com</p>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
</Layout>
